        </div>
        <div class="flex-auto">
          <h5 class="h3 mt0 mb1 regular dark-blue">P.J. Onori</h5>
          <h5 class="h4 mt0 mb1 med-gray regular">
              Designer
          </h5>
          <p class="med-gray">I'm a design technologist living in San Francisco. I have worked for companies such as Adaptive Path, Method and Current TV and worked with clients including the United Nations, Samsung, Adobe, TED.com and Foodspotting. I am a long-time supporter of open source and have several of my own including <a href="https://github.com/somerandomdude/Frank" target="_blank">Frank</a>, <a href="https://useiconic.com" target="_blank">Iconic</a> and <a href="https://thenounproject.com/somerandomdude/collection/cue/" target="_blank">Cue</a>. <a href="http://twitter.com/somerandomdude" target="_blank">Follow me on Twitter</a>.</p>
        </div>
